  "Description": {
    "English": "A technology module harvested from the remains of a large interstellar starship. May be collected from <span class=\"name name-stellar\">freighter crashsites</span> or salvaged during <span class=\"name name-stellar\">frigate expeditions</span>.<br><br>Useless in its current form, a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Research Station</span> aboard your freighter may be able to convert it into useable technology.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "取自大型飞船残骸的一种技术模块。可以从<span class=\"name name-stellar\">货船坠毁地点</span>收集，或在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">护卫舰远征</span>期间回收。<br><br>当前状态下毫无用处，你货船上的<span class=\"name name-technology\">研究站</span>也许能把它转化成可用的技术。",
    "TencentChinese": "取自大型飞船残骸的一种技术模块。可以从<span class=\"name name-stellar\">货船坠毁地点</span>收集，或在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">护卫舰远征</span>期间回收。<br><br>当前状态下毫无用处，你货船上的<span class=\"name name-technology\">研究站</span>也许能把它转化成可用的技术。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "從一艘大型星際太空船收集的科技模組。可以從<span class=\"name name-stellar\">貨船失事地點</span>收集，也可以在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">巡防艦探勘</span>中回收。<br><br>目前形式無法使用，但貨船上的<span class=\"name name-technology\">研究站</span>或許可以將其轉換成有用的科技。"
  },
